cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY

This paper is about robotic mapping, which is a subfield of robotics. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the use of laser and sonar data, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a probabilistic mapping technique, which involves probability distributions and sampling techniques, indicating a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with the problem of motion planning, which is a key issue in control systems (cs.SY).
